Tokenade is proprietary software (the npm package `@tokenade/cli`).

This repository contains the public npm launcher and installer for the
Tokenade CLI, published for transparency and inspection. The files here
(`bin/tokenade.js`, `install.js`, `package.json`) may be read and audited.

Tokenade is a freemium product (a free tier plus a paid Pro plan). The
Tokenade CLI binary itself is NOT distributed in this repository — it is
downloaded at install time from the signed release manifest at
https://downloads.tokenade.net and verified by SHA-256.

